# NETWORK::NETWORK_SET_TRANSITION_VISIBILITY_LOCK

## Parameters
* **BOOL** lockVisibility
* **BOOL** lockSetting

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Lock session visibility.
bLockVisibility - Locked or not
bLockSetting - Locked to be visible or not
